Man, I love Muay Thai, both as a combat sport and as a martial arts discipline. It has always been my first love, as I trained Muay Thai well before transitioning to an MMA gym. With that said, as a father, seeing small children doing full-contact fighting on a professional level is really frightening. It is the national sport of Thailand, and is absolutely ingrained in their culture, but it's really hard to watch kids as young as 8 taking that kind of damage before their brains have even come close to being fully developed.
